{"tid":374094,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【新手改詞】試填《披風》粵語版本","createTime":"2017-08-25T13:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T08:13:28.000Z","uid":37464,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"998f4e27290c6a64a7646ee510442616d5ea738a","tid":374094,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:25:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://youtu.be/idU_BBgRqME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FidU_BBgRqME&d=SnmMeHn8PT6itnnsxCWLn8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=a5c05e0c\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/idU_BBgRqME</a><br />\n<br />\n原詞：易家揚 I 作曲：MJ 譚傑明、Jerald<br />\n改詞：DC_<br />\n演唱：Herman Wong<br />\n歌名：被窩［粵語］（OT：披風）<br />\n<br />\n歡送會　你可有記得　餐桌中你傾吐的事<br />\n來日要發奮努力改變　不要像以前<br />\n轉眼間　襯衫似皺紙　場境已變<br />\n你舉杯無言　藏著了以往愛玩把戲那張臉<br />\n<br />\n時間尚會在匆匆走過　何以落魄後躺在被窩<br />\n咖啡陪坐　獨自哼歌　也許人愈大更怕風浪<br />\n愈想輕鬆一點抗拒難過<br />\n等到淚腺枯乾　學會假裝<br />\n<br />\n當每天有新戲上演　好與醜也總會出現<br />\n難道怕上鏡應付改變　就忘掉語言<br />\n想太多會消耗半天　如果要餘生也入眠<br />\n沿路錯過了　幾多歡笑　看不見  <br />\n<br />\n時間尚會在匆匆走過　何以落魄後躺在被窩<br />\n咖啡陪坐　獨自哼歌　也許人愈大更怕風浪<br />\n愈想輕鬆一點抗拒難過<br />\n搬到夢裡觀光<br />\n<br />\n難過是靠著雙手摔破　何以落魄後躺在被窩<br />\n固執如我實在不多　決不能掉下老友一個<br />\n折返到最初　就算不可<br />\n不要緊　路有許多"},{"pid":"cd1c91635ffb0ca152a4263439498a8d4ca06948","tid":374094,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:26:01.000Z","msg":"新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db5077ff8e84ed8c82d694adafcd2409a331157","tid":374094,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a72031aacd77df88c15cc967de34a5e5ca2de5","tid":374094,"uid":40429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:28:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" cl